high_descs: Turn right and step forward to face the sink.
Pick up the knife on the sink.
Look right to face the knife in the sink.
Cut the apple in the sink into pieces.
Turn right and walk forward to face the cabinet to the right of the fridge.
Place the knife in the cabinet to the right of the fridge.
Turn around and step forward to face the sink.
Pick up a piece of apple in the sink.
Turn around and walk forward to face the fridge.
Cool the apple piece in the fridge and remove it.
Turn right and cross the room and turn left to face the microwave.
Place the apple piece in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: To cool an apple piece and place it in the microwave.

high_descs: Go to the drying rack left of the sink.
Pick up the knife in the drying rack.
Move to the sink on the right.
Slice the apple in the sink.
Go to the cabinet right of the fridge.
Put the knife  in the cabinet.
Go back to the sink.
Pick up an apple slice in the sink.
Go to the fridge.
Chill the apple slice in the fridge.
Take the cold apple slice to the microwave.
Put the apple slice in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold apple slice in the microwave.
